```
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Color Palette</h2>
        <div class="color-palette">
            <div class="color-swatch neon-pink">NEON PINK</div>
            <div class="color-swatch electric-purple">ELECTRIC PURPLE</div>
            <div class="color-swatch cyber-blue">CYBER BLUE</div>
            <div class="color-swatch acid-green">ACID GREEN</div>
            <div class="color-swatch danger-yellow">DANGER YELLOW</div>
        </div>
        <p>The palette shifts and warps throughout episodes, with colors bleeding into each other during drug sequences and intense emotional moments. Backgrounds pulse with living gradients that respond to the characters' psychological states.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Core Characters</h2>
        <div class="character-grid">
            <div class="character-card">
                <div class="character-name">BLIMPO <span class="mood-indicator chaotic"></span></div>
                <div class="balloon-visual">
                    <div class="blimpo-balloon"></div>
                    <div class="string"></div>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Head:</strong> Over-inflated red heart balloon, straining with visible stress cracks</p>
                <p><strong>Body:</strong> Lanky punk in leather jacket, swaggering gait</p>
                <p><strong>String:</strong> Thick, fraying rope constantly snagging</p>
                <p><strong>Voice:</strong> Manic, high-pitched when excited, crackling like overstretched rubber</p>
                <p><strong>Animation:</strong> Bounces uncontrollably, floats into objects, head creaks audibly when stressed</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="character-card">
                <div class="character-name">FLOP <span class="mood-indicator melancholic"></span></div>
                <div class="balloon-visual">
                    <div class="flop-balloon"></div>
                    <div class="string"></div>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Head:</strong> Deflated blue starfish balloon, drooping like a sad hood</p>
                <p><strong>Body:</strong> Curvy figure in thrift store dress, perpetual slouch</p>
                <p><strong>String:</strong> Tangled thread that trips her up</p>
                <p><strong>Voice:</strong> Low, raspy, like a jazz singer who's seen too much</p>
                <p><strong>Animation:</strong> Sluggish movements, head sways with melancholic weight</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="character-card">
                <div class="character-name">POPPY <span class="mood-indicator paranoid"></span></div>
                <div class="balloon-visual">
                    <div class="poppy-balloon"></div>
                    <div class="string"></div>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Head:</strong> Shredded green dinosaur balloon, jagged rubber scraps</p>
                <p><strong>Body:</strong> Wiry frame in ripped tank top, covered in bandages</p>
                <p><strong>String:</strong> Chewed-up mess he constantly fidgets with</p>
                <p><strong>Voice:</strong> Rapid-fire bursts, paranoid conspiracy theorist energy</p>
                <p><strong>Animation:</strong> Twitchy, erratic movements, scraps flutter dramatically</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="character-card">
                <div class="character-name">ZEPPY <span class="mood-indicator optimistic"></span></div>
                <div class="balloon-visual">
                    <div class="zeppy-balloon"></div>
                    <div class="string"></div>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Head:</strong> Yellow giraffe balloon with wobbly spots, long neck</p>
                <p><strong>Body:</strong> Athletic build in neon tracksuit, ready for action</p>
                <p><strong>String:</strong> Glittery rainbow cord, obsessively polished</p>
                <p><strong>Voice:</strong> Bubbly but street-smart, slight helium pitch</p>
                <p><strong>Animation:</strong> Graceful despite awkward head, neck sways hypnotically</p>
